[I] Multichannel AM/NFM demodulator

[T] RTLSDR-Airband receives analog radio voice channels and produces audio
[T] streams which can be routed to various outputs, such as online streaming
[T] services like LiveATC.net.

[U] https://github.com/rtl-airband/RTLSDR-Airband

